Woo hoo!  I got the files!  Igot the files!  *Dances around all happy and stuff*  Woo hoo!  I'm a happy camping Viking!  Woo hoo!

ahem...umm...oops....

Polt/Frodo

Greetings and salutations everyone!

Things are finally going better now that I've withdrawn from this freakin' math class.  Funny, I thought the quick paced summer semester was over and done with.  This prof has been running through the stuff at lightning speed!  Hello?  I'm lost, I think I'm still on the first page.......hmmm  Oh well.
I went and talked to a lady today who thinks I can get one of my math classes transferred to the Uni so I won't have to take anymore of this B.S.  just concentrate on the history....I mean, it IS my major, afterall.  What a crock this Uni is.  However, if this works, I'll be sure to throw a party!
Okay, it's getting late and I'm exhausted so I'm going to hide in my book case now. 

Love ya all!
Polt   *POUF*
